---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About – CraveSmart"
  description="Learn more about CraveSmart and the mission behind the recipes."
>
  <section class="bg-white text-gray-900 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-center">
        About CraveSmart
      </h1>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <img
          src="/placeholders/image.png"
          alt="Isabella, creator of CraveSmart"
          class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-full shadow-xl object-cover"
        />

        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Hi, I'm Isabella, the creator of CraveSmart. I built this site because I love food, but I also care about how it fits into real life, real goals, and real cravings.
          </p>

          <p>
            CraveSmart is all about viral recipes that actually deliver — meals and treats that taste incredible, feel satisfying, and still work with smarter macros.
          </p>

          <p>
            From quick breakfasts and easy dinners to snacks and desserts worth making again, everything here is curated to help you enjoy food without overcomplicating it.
          </p>

          <p class="font-medium text-tiffany">
            Cook smarter, crave boldly, and make indulgence work for you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>